      <title>揭秘Aave可升级合约漏洞 - 代理模式下的致命缺陷</title>
      <link>https://qife122.github.io/p/%E6%8F%AD%E7%A7%98aave%E5%8F%AF%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E5%90%88%E7%BA%A6%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E-%E4%BB%A3%E7%90%86%E6%A8%A1%E5%BC%8F%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%84%E8%87%B4%E5%91%BD%E7%BC%BA%E9%99%B7/</link>
